summary: Here’s a toast to my real friends & one year of reputation. ✨🥂
body:
Here’s a toast to my real friends & one year of reputation. ✨🥂

The fact that Taylor is happy at the moment is so uplifting. It has really rubbed off on me. I wish that we could sit around with her and talk shit and drink moscato over a fig and cheese board platter. Here’s a toast to my real friends. ✨🥂🍓
